    <abstract>
      <t>&lt;p&gt;This document specifies the requirements for the provision of security services to the HyperText Transport Protocol.  These services include confidentiality, integrity, user authentication, and authentication of servers/services, including proxied or gatewayed services.  This memo provides information for the Internet community.  This memo does not specify an Internet standard of any kind.&lt;/p&gt;</t>
